Plans for 0.3.0
===============

  W = Work in progress
  D = Done
  P = Postponed
  ? = Questionable


Plans after 0.2.0
=================

  * Find, find and replace
      - Regular expressions
          o Support all Python regular expression flags
      - Simple string search
          o Match case
          o Match entire word only
      - Target
          o Selection / current project / all open projects
          o Main text, translation text
      - Bar (gtk.Box) or dialog?
      - gtk.CellRenderer.start_editing(...) and gtk.Editable.select_region(...)
        on match


Unscheduled
===========

  * Documentation (HTML)

  * Support for additional subtitle formats

