        http://www.mplayerhq.hu/DOCS/tech/mpsub.sub

      - SubViewer & SubViewer 2.0

      - SubStation Alpha (SSA & ASS)
        http://moodub.free.fr/ass-specs.doc

      - SAMI
        http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/en-us/dnacc/html/atg_samiarticle.asp
